# LYONiX Monad

**A cryptographic provenance engine built from Geometry.**

I am not a professional developer. What I understand deeply is a certain **Geometry** — a mathematical structure centered on order, time, identity, and relationships.

Using AI assistance, I translated this Geometry into the LYONiX Monad — a lightweight system for tracking creation, derivation, and attribution in the age of powerful AI.

### Purpose
The Monad helps solve real provenance problems:
- Proving "I created this first"
- Detecting derivatives with temporal awareness
- Generating compliance hashes for regulatory requirements (EU AI Act, California TDTA)
- Supporting fair attribution without exposing trade secrets

### Demo

Run the improved single-file demo to see the Monad in action:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ErikLYONiX/lyonix-suite.git
cd lyonix-suite
pip install numpy
python lyonix_demo.py